{"tid":2368595,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"運房局申追加撥款  港珠澳橋再超支貼15億 建制盲撐：世紀工程","createTime":"2021-01-16T10:30:53.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-16T10:46:39.000Z","uid":25558,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"f9364e04b0f6f73d13ea6f335f61788a6191c477","tid":2368595,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-16T10:30:53.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210116/BSB6MK42QRAQLGTHZUZA4W7PLI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210116%2FBSB6MK42QRAQLGTHZUZA4W7PLI%2F&d=urW02bDNsyUCiNuSwPhOyBq8xf71D2STVxQEH8iwqLk%3D&h=4564d09a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210116%2FBSB6MK42QRAQLGTHZUZA4W7PLI%2F&h=2a923125\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210116/BSB6MK42QRAQLGTHZUZA4W7PLI/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n運房局申追加撥款 <br />\n港珠澳橋再超支貼15億 建制盲撐：世紀工程<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/nUHFSzFvIda0xm_rH6wxk1lwL2g=/3985x2657/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/F3N7D2P3VFAPBJ52SCENHRNFIA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FnUHFSzFvIda0xm_rH6wxk1lwL2g%3D%2F3985x2657%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FF3N7D2P3VFAPBJ52SCENHRNFIA.jpg&h=b26a6828&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■港珠澳大橋再次超支，坊間質疑是大白象工程。資料圖片<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】港珠澳大橋屢次超支，即使已經通車，港人仍要繼續為這個國家級大白象埋單。運房局昨向立法會申請主橋工程追加撥款，涉款約15億港元。立法會則發揮其橡皮圖章功能，昨日討論撥款時，多名建制派議員盛讚港珠澳大橋為「世紀工程」，對撥款表示理解和支持。委員會主席易志明最終以會上未有明顯反對聲音為由，項目將轉交工務小組審議。民主黨副主席林卓廷直斥保皇黨盲撐港珠澳大橋，卻未有考慮基建有否惠及公眾，形容「條橋起完都冇人用，幾宏偉都冇用啦」。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：三度攤大手板 涉160億公帑<br />\n<br />\n路政署主要工程管理處處長黃劍波表示，粵港澳三地政府2008年同意共同承擔建造大橋主橋的費用，其中港府須負擔67.5億元人民幣。其後當局於2009年初斥資2.33億港元作工程初步設計，並於同年向立法會財委會申請撥款90.465。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n黃劍波續解釋，政府按照2009年三地的出資額比例計算，港府須額外承擔24億元港元，。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/yyyr85VhLQf4lHyHAOsqDzfNaQk=/1421x886/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/KJRQAUFE2JFPJP3KV63E5LTRRE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fyyyr85VhLQf4lHyHAOsqDzfNaQk%3D%2F1421x886%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FKJRQAUFE2JFPJP3KV63E5LTRRE.jpg&h=f19fb5e0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n陳 帆<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/xQBK3PO6VuaIPG5z0lw6rOghOzk=/1093x693/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/GC6WCZ5GBFGNVLKWH6OCD6LOBI.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FxQBK3PO6VuaIPG5z0lw6rOghOzk%3D%2F1093x693%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FGC6WCZ5GBFGNVLKWH6OCD6LOBI.jpg&h=56f487e3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/yo9cbLkV-bDVsc2gWDRggs9glKs=/1057x244/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/JNOFBDWPGVD47I3J6OJSNZKVFQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fyo9cbLkV-bDVsc2gWDRggs9glKs%3D%2F1057x244%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FJNOFBDWPGVD47I3J6OJSNZKVFQ.jpg&h=507d22ce&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n陳帆聲稱最後結算<br />\n<br />\n運房局局長陳帆補充，由於主橋工程龐大而複雜，施工難度比預期大，加上人工和材料價格上漲等因素影響，使建設成本在後期有所增加，因此向立法會提出追加撥款。他聲稱是次撥款已是最後結算，三地政府暫無討論再向工程注資。<br />\n<br />\n立法會文件顯示，主橋工程超支主要涉及三方面的建造費用調整，包括資源投入標準的更新、工程變更以及工資和材料價格調整。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n工程變更涉款約33億元人民幣，是。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n林卓廷：起完冇人用<br />\n<br />\n港珠澳大橋雖然再次超支，但多名保皇黨卻讚口不絕。旅遊界姚思榮會上表示，港珠澳大橋屬「世紀工程，全世界都注目」，明白工程涉及複雜工序，超支雖不理想但感理解，對撥款表示支持。<br />\n<br />\n建築、測量及都市規劃界謝偉銓亦形容大橋為世紀工程，認為工程的複雜性「前所未有」，故建造時間和造價受影響是可以理解。立。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n前立法會議員毛孟靜批評，港珠澳大橋是港府為達到政治目的而建造的大白象工程，「。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n民主黨副主席林卓廷亦炮轟保皇黨盲撐港珠澳大橋，強調基建應考慮社會效益，但。。。。。。"},{"pid":"a6b3c7c9df5ad35fea2e12cfaa730404925f16b0","tid":2368595,"uid":15567,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-16T10:40:40.000Z","msg":"太少<br />\n應該追撥1500億<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/nope.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6012ca24b6c362ad987b422bd90bc455b5b34aaa","tid":2368595,"uid":284855,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a6b3c7c9df5ad35fea2e12cfaa730404925f16b0","tid":2368595,"uid":15567,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-16T10:40:40.000Z","msg":"太少<br />\n應該追撥1500億<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/nope.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-16T10:42:19.000Z","msg":"咪係，加稅<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce24b8d6da083e839858e259ebccbe4ba85ca8c5","tid":2368595,"uid":31863,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a6b3c7c9df5ad35fea2e12cfaa730404925f16b0","tid":2368595,"uid":15567,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-16T10:40:40.000Z","msg":"太少<br />\n應該追撥1500億<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/nope.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-16T10:45:13.000Z","msg":"加夠15000億我覺得唔過份<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f4db059df77ade978dbb2282dbf6d7060ef3c61","tid":2368595,"uid":119609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-16T10:46:39.000Z","msg":"入面全部都係你嘅人，你要幾多咪出聲囉唔洗解釋架喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}